{
  "texts": [
    "However, the effectiveness of GenAI as an educational tool depends significantly on how teachers guide student interactions with these systems.",
    "To answer this question, this study investigates the capabilities of two leading LLMs, Google's Bard and OpenAI's ChatGPT 4.0, in the context of coastal ecosystem education.",
    "By comparatively analyzing their responses to a set of relevant questions, this research aims to contribute to the growing understanding of LLMs' potential in environmental science education and scientific communication.",
    "Technical Competency of AI SystemsTo evaluate the technical competency of AI systems, the performance of Google's Bard, leveraging the Gemini model, can be compared against OpenAI's ChatGPT 4.0 across several benchmarks that are critical in simulating complex cognitive tasks.",
    "The Gemini model demonstrates exceptional proficiency in the Multi-Task Language Understanding (MMLU) benchmark with a score of 90.0%, reflecting its robustness in understanding and answering questions across 57 varied subjects, including STEM, humanities, and more."
  ]
}